# Normalize line endings: store text as LF in the repo and check it out as LF
# on every platform. Overrides a global core.autocrlf=true, which was checking
# files out as CRLF and breaking WSL/Linux tooling. `text=auto` auto-detects
# text vs binary; `eol=lf` forces LF on text files. Binaries are marked
# explicitly so they are never touched.
* text=auto eol=lf

*.sh text eol=lf

# Explicit binaries (never line-ending-converted).
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.webp binary
*.avif binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.otf binary
*.eot binary
*.pdf binary
*.zip binary
*.gz binary
